Join the Hoochies of Houston at the Essence Festival of Culture for an opportunity to connect with community organizations, celebrate culture, and access resources that support health, wellness, and empowerment. While you're there, be sure to stop by the Hoochies of Houston table to pick up Plan C materials, abortion pills by mail resources, and free mini swag, and connect with trusted information about abortion pills by mail and the work being done to expand access in communities across the country.
